name: Hashkill
description: 76370c8b218eacfdf6a33bd4c311575a is the md5 of the flag (remember the format of the flag: stuyctf{XXX_XXXXXXXXXXX_XXXXX}). It comprises a number between 0 and 1000, an underscore, a borough of New York City, another underscore, and a number between 10000 and 15000.
hint: All characters are lowercase! This should decrease the number of hashes to check.
